  "prompt": "If I delete my Tinder account and uninstall the app, does my profile still show to those I've matched with?",
  "response": "If you delete your Tinder account and uninstall the app, your profile will no longer be visible to anyone, including those you've matched with. When you delete your account, it removes all your data, including your matches and messages. However, it might take a bit of time for the app to fully update and reflect this change. Once your account is deleted, the matches will see that your profile is no longer available.",
